%% Diagram: Each Interface Layer Adds Specific Capabilities While Inheriting All Parent Func
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    A[EventTarget] -->|adds| B[Event System]
    C[Node] -->|adds| D[Tree Operations]
    E[Element] -->|adds| F[Attributes & Selectors]
    G[HTMLElement] -->|adds| H[HTML Semantics]

    B --> addEventListener
    B --> dispatchEvent

    D --> parentNode
    D --> childNodes
    D --> appendChild

    F --> querySelector
    F --> getAttribute
    F --> classList

    H --> contentEditable
    H --> dataset
    H --> innerText
